                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10112" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0303</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">341 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美美与共：中泰证券文化建设实践创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Beauty in Harmony: The Innovative Journey of Zhongtai Securities in Corporate Culture Construction</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王洪生，李发菊，刘素莉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东农业大学*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中泰证券股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中泰证券；文化建设；党建引领；员工关怀</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhongtai Securities; Corporate Culture Construction; Party Building Leadership; Employee Care</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦中泰证券以“美美与共”为核心价值观的文化建设实践。2015 年起，在经济与金融改革背景下，中泰证券开启文化建设征程，历经初步探索、体系形成，至2023年深化确立“美美与共”价值观。该价值观传承创新行业文化理念，融入“忠诚、创新”元素，强调协同发展。在践行过程中，公司多管齐下。内部强化员工培训与关怀，借主题教育提升合规意识，优化福利、创新考核激发员工活力；持续开展投资者教育，通过“投教大篷车黄河行”等活动普及金融知识。外部深化与企业合作，如与枣庄市开展“共成之行”活动，助力地方经济。文化建设成效显著，2023年公司营收、利润大幅增长。然而，中泰证券也面临公司识别系统不完善、外部宣传能力不足等问题。本案例旨在为金融企业文化建设提供借鉴，启发思考如何提升核心竞争力、实现可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on the corporate culture construction practice of Zhongtai Securities with the core value of &quot;Mei Mei Yu Gong&quot; (Harmony and Co - growth). Since 2015, against the backdrop of economic and financial reforms, Zhongtai Securities has embarked on the journey of corporate culture construction. After initial exploration and system formation, it deeply established the &quot;Mei Mei Yu Gong&quot; value in 2023. This value inherits and innovates the industry&#39;s cultural concept, incorporates elements of &quot;loyalty and innovation&quot;, and emphasizes collaborative development.In the process of practicing this value, the company has taken multiple measures. Internally, it has strengthened employee training and care. It has enhanced employees&#39; compliance awareness through theme - based education, optimized benefits, and innovated performance appraisals to stimulate employees&#39; vitality. It has continuously carried out investor education, popularizing financial knowledge through activities such as the &quot;Investor Education Caravan along the Yellow River&quot;. Externally, it has deepened cooperation with enterprises. For example, it launched the &quot;Gong Cheng Zhi Xing&quot; (Journey to Success Together) activity with Zaozhuang City to boost the local economy.The corporate culture construction has achieved remarkable results. In 2023, the company&#39;s revenue and profits increased significantly. However, Zhongtai Securities also faces problems such as an imperfect corporate identity system and insufficient external publicity capabilities. This case aims to provide references for the corporate culture construction of financial enterprises and inspire thinking on how to enhance core competitiveness and achieve sustainable development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《现代企业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织文化理论；组织绩效理论；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
